<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٠٧٤- مَعرُور، الكَلبِيُّ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>عَنْ عُثمان.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وقَالَ بعضهم:</span> عَنْ عُمَر؛ فِي الذَّبيحة.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>رَوَى عَنه يَحيى بْن أَبي كَثِير، والأَوزاعِيُّ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>